</p>

@BGRND{{}}
<p>
@HI{{@EM{{kotohanai}}}} can sometimes mean both "no need" and "no possibility": in this case context will determine the interpretation.

<table class="sentence">
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      @HI{{@FG{{@KJ{{old*boy}}:kimi}}ga@KJ{{come}}ru@EM{{kotohanai}}to@KJ{{think}}imasu.}}
